<section id="profitCenter">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>profit centers</primary>

      <secondary>adding new numbers for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Profit Center Number</title>

  <para>To add a new profit center number, select the
  <guibutton>NEW</guibutton> button. The following screen will appear:</para>

  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/profitCenter.png"/>
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Create New Profit Center Number</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>

  <para>When creating a new profit center number, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Number</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a number to identify the profit center.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Description</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter a brief description of the profit center.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
